OL,3,CChristian sacked over online posts
OL,4,Csays she is 'not alone' ahead of appeal
OL,6,FA Court of Appeal challenge to a
OL,7,Fschool worker's dismissal over
OL,8,FFacebook posts criticising plans to
OL,9,Fteach about LGBT+ relationships in
OL,10,Fschools has begun.
OL,12,FKristie Higgs was dismissed for gross
OL,13,Fmisconduct by Farmor's School, in
OL,14,FFairford, Gloucestershire, in 2019.
OL,16,FThe decision came after she shared and
OL,17,Fcommented on posts which raised
OL,18,Fconcerns about relationship education
OL,19,Fat her son's Church of England primary
OL,20,Fschool.
