OL,3,CChristian sacked over online posts
OL,4,Csays she is 'not alone' ahead of appeal
OL,6,FOne of the posts referred to
OL,7,F"brainwashing our children".
OL,9,FThe 47-year-old from Fairford appealed
OL,10,Fagainst that judgment to the
OL,11,FEmployment Appeal Tribunal in London,
OL,12,Fwhich ruled in her favour but remitted
OL,13,Fthe case to an employment tribunal for
OL,14,Fa fresh determination.
OL,16,FHer lawyers are now appealing the
OL,17,Fdecision to order a new tribunal
OL,18,Fhearing and won the right to have her
OL,19,Fcase heard by the Court of Appeal
OL,20,Fjudges earlier this year.
