OL,3,CChristian sacked over online posts
OL,4,Csays she is 'not alone' ahead of appeal
OL,6,FSpeaking outside the Royal Courts of
OL,7,FJustice before the hearing on
OL,8,FWednesday 2 October, Mrs Higgs said
OL,9,Fshe was "thankful to God for
OL,10,Fsustaining (her)".
OL,12,F"I am not alone to be treated this
OL,13,Fway. Many of the others here to
OL,14,Fsupport me today have faced similar
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,17,F"This is not just about me. It cannot
OL,18,Fbe right that so many Christians are
OL,19,Flosing their jobs or facing discipline
OL,20,Ffor sharing biblical truth, our
OL,21,FChristian beliefs."
