OL,3,CChristian sacked over online posts
OL,4,Csays she is 'not alone' ahead of appeal
OL,6,FMrs Higgs and her supporters also held
OL,7,Fa group prayer before entering the
OL,8,Fcourt building.
OL,10,FThe case came after pupils were to
OL,11,Flearn about the No Outsiders In Our
OL,12,FSchool programme, which comprises of a
OL,13,Fseries of books aimed at teaching
OL,14,Fprimary school children about the
OL,15,FEquality Act..
OL,17,FMrs Higgs, who was posting on Facebook
OL,18,Funder her maiden name, shared two
OL,19,Fposts in October 2018 to about 100
OL,20,Ffriends, one of which referred to
OL,21,F"brainwashing our children".
