OL,3,CChristian sacked over online posts
OL,4,Csays she is 'not alone' ahead of appeal
OL,6,FIn its ruling in 2020, the tribunal
OL,7,Fconcluded her religion was a
OL,8,F"protected characteristic" as defined
OL,9,Fby the Equality Act, but the school
OL,10,Fdismissed her lawfully.
OL,12,FThe appeal hearing at the Royal Courts
OL,13,Fof Justice in London is expected to
OL,14,Fconclude on Thursday 3 October.
